  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil or ghee in a large pan over medium heat.",
    "Add cumin seeds and let them sizzle for a few seconds.",
    "Add chopped onion and sauté until translucent.",
    "Add grated ginger and minced garlic and sauté for another minute.",
    "Add red chili powder, turmeric powder, and coriander powder, and sauté for 1 minute.",
    "Add red lentils, salt, and 4 cups of water, and bring to a boil.",
